qDef.qDef:
Count(
{$<
[Item Origin Description]= {'FG Development'},    Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , [Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, 

[Customer Key]={'=(sum({$<    [Month ID]={"<=$(=$(v_Max_Month_ID))"}, Year={$(v_Max_Year)} >} [Invoice Amount USD])>0)'}>}

Distinct [Customer Key])

Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Dev)
	,Count( {$< [Item Origin Description]= {'FG Development'},  Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , [Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'},  [Customer Key]={'=(sum({1<[Month ID]={"<=$(=$(v_Max_Month_ID))"}, Year={$(v_Max_Year)} >} [Invoice Amount USD])>0)'}>}  Distinct [Customer Key])
	, Sum({$<[Item Origin Description]= {'FG Development'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} ,  Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
	,(Sum({$<[Item Origin Description]= {'FG Development'},  [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate]))/1000
 	,(Sum({$<[Item Origin Description]= {'FG Development'},  [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},
             [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
             
             
 -Sum({$<[Item Origin Description]= {'FG Development'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},
              [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate]))
              
              
            /1000       

       
)
